text: Cage the Elephant is an American rock band. They were formed in 2006 in Bowling Green, Kentucky. They moved to England and settled in London in 2008, shortly before their self-titled first album was released. The band currently consists of Matt Shultz, his older brother Brad Shult, Nick Bockrath, Matthan Minster, Daniel Tichenor, and Jared Champion.
